</figure>

<p><a href="http://userscripts.org/scripts/source/76281.user.js" class="button"><em>↯</em> Install the overwrite styles</a></p>

<p><em>On Safari, you&#8217;ll need <a href="http://8-p.info/greasekit/">Greasekit</a> installed.<br />
  On Firefox, you&#8217;ll need <a href="http://www.greasespot.net/">Greasemonkey</a>.<br />
  On Chrome, it should just work straight out of the box.</em></p>

<p>You can preview the userscript here:<br />
  <a href="http://userscripts.org/scripts/review/76281">http://userscripts.org/scripts/review/76281</a></p> 
